  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> [06.06.2025]</p>

  <p>Welcome to <strong>ozonehotel.net</strong> (“we”, “our”, or “us”). We are committed to protecting your personal data and ensuring your privacy when you visit our website or use our services.</p>

  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Personal information:</strong> Name, email, phone number, and booking details.</li>
    <li><strong>Technical data:</strong> IP address, browser type, device info, and activity via cookies.</li>
    <li><strong>Payment information:</strong> Processed securely through third-party systems (we don’t store full payment details).</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To process bookings and manage reservations</li>
    <li>To communicate with you regarding inquiries or stays</li>
    <li>To improve website functionality and user experience</li>
    <li>To send promotional offers (if you opted in)</li>
    <li>To comply with legal requirements</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Data Security</h2>
  <p>We implement appropriate measures to protect your data. However, no method of online transmission is completely secure.</p>

  <h2>4. Sharing of Information</h2>
  <p>We do not sell your data. We may share it with:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Trusted third-party providers (e.g., booking or payment services)</li>
    <li>Authorities if required by law</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>5. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
  <p>We use cookies to improve functionality and collect analytics. You can disable cookies in your browser settings.</p>

  <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
  <p>You have the right to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Access your personal data</li>
    <li>Request corrections or deletions</li>
    <li>Withdraw consent where applicable</li>
    <li>Object to certain types of processing</li>
  </ul>
  <p>Contact us to exercise these rights: <a href="mailto:info@ozonehotel.net">info@ozonehotel.net</a></p>

  <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Updates will be posted here with the revised date.</p>

  <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
  <p>If you have any questions, please contact us at:</p>
  <p>Email: <a href="mailto:info@ozonehotel.net">info@ozonehotel.net</a><br>
